  19th century thumb|statue of the montgolfier brothers ( 1883 - 1885 )   during the first half of the 19th century , the need for an industrial workforce for paper - making and leather at annonay attracted population from the surrounding countryside .

french bred : after their births in 1740 & 1745 in annonay , france , things were up , up & away for these brothers

